Sunday 16 September

7:30PM

Henning Wehn

Nina Conti

Jayde Adams

Phil Wang

Fin Taylor

Self styled German Comedy Ambassador Henning Wehn headlines the final show of Bristol Comedy Garden 2018. Expect a hit packed set from the Would I Lie To You Star, chock-full of inimitable teutonic jolliness.

Wehn wraps his vowels around the issues of immigration and identity. And he triumphs at it

The Times
Joining Henning is groundbreaking ventriloquist and British Comedy Award winner Nina Conti, plus fast-rising Bristolian Jayde Adams, Have I Got News For You star Phil Wang makes his Comedy Garden debut, and the wildly acclaimed Fin Taylor hosts.
